      "timestamp": "08:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "可爱呀！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "收到新表情，立马发给你了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "[[sticker:uploads/upload_1771889353808527031.jpg]]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh我直接一个偷走",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "请好好使用吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "我这边今天下雨了诶",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "下雨不是很正常吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "有必要下雨也提一嘴吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "一般下雪天很少会下雨的。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "下雨的雪天会特别湿冷，让我想起南方的冬天",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "那么问题来了，下雪天下雨到底是下雪还是下雨？好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "雨夹雪",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "天气正在回暖。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，不是应该更冷吗？怎么回暖了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为回暖了，所以才没有变成冰雪落下来啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "冷天下雨更冷，作为一个资深南方人，你应该懂啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "太湿了，感觉我要变成蘑菇了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "那每到回南天我就会变成蘑菇",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "你好啊，小蘑菇",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh还蛮可爱的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我要做花菇",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我做秀珍菇",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "为啥是秀珍菇",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "秀珍菇好吃啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你是觉得花菇好吃吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得花姑很漂亮",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "这让我想起云南人吃伞伞躺板板",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "最漂亮的菇一般都是最有毒的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "你知道毒蝇伞菇吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "这是什么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "一听就毒性好强。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "你去搜搜",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "长得很像是童话里的蘑菇",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "哎呦我去",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "这不就是童话里的蘑菇吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊，童话里的是照着画的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "我，那谁是第一个吃了这个蘑菇才知道不能吃的人呢？？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "这个我还真没查过有没有记载？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "不过这个蘑菇跟百草枯一样，一旦使用，必死无疑",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "老师，你写武侠吗？",
