      "timestamp": "08:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "正打算看呢。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "这段时间这个剧超火",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "你要替我先试试毒吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得可以看啊，我已经看了两集了",
